  </p>
  <p>
   <b>Internal forces</b>
  </p>
  <p>Bending</p>
  <p>
   <span class="eq">
    <var>M</var>
    <sub>a</sub>
    =
    <span class="dvc">
     <var>M</var>
     <span class="dvl">
     </span>
     <var>l</var>
    </span>
    ·
    <var>a</var>
    =
    <span class="dvc">
     10
     <span class="dvl">
     </span>
     5
    </span>
    · 2 = 4
   </span>
   kN·m
  </p>
  <p>
   <span class="eq">
    <var>M</var>
    <sub>b</sub>
    =
